minutes, here you go.

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:38.390
ALEXIS: So what you're saying,
is the technology is the same,

00:05:38.390 --> 00:05:40.520
packaging technologies
are the same,

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:43.440
